  "GEMINI.md": "# snap-proj — Gemini CLI context

Project context for Gemini CLI. For cross-tool context see \`AGENTS.md\`.

## Available skills (cross-tool)

This project contains a library of AI skills in \`.claude/skills/\`. The skills are plain markdown and apply to every AI tool, including Gemini CLI. When the user's task matches a skill's description, read the corresponding \`SKILL.md\` and follow its instructions.

